@notice Calculates the start and end BTC output amounts for the auction.
 @param startsBTCperBTCRate The starting sBTC per BTC rate (WAD 1e18).
 @param endcbsBTCperBTCRate The ending sBTC per BTC rate (WAD 1e18).
